PrecisAmendment to the ATLANTIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1985 dividing Lobster Fishing Area (LFA) 31 into two distinct fishing areas: one east of Flying Point where spring ice conditions are a problem (LFA 31A), and one west of Flying Point where spring ice has not been a problem (LFA 31B).

precis:
Amendment to the ATLANTIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1985 dividing Lobster
Fishing Area (LFA) 31 into two distinct fishing areas: one east of Flying
Point where spring ice conditions are a problem (LFA 31A), and one west of
Flying Point where spring ice has not been a problem (LFA 31B).
